# CSS tooling (mandatory)

When creating or changing **any** `.css` file, **read and apply** the global **`responsive-css`** skill (`~/.cursor/skills/responsive-css/SKILL.md` or invoke `@responsive-css`).

Standards: mobile-first, nested `@media`, breakpoints `768px` and `1024px`, custom properties for breakpoint overrides, `clamp` / container queries where appropriate, logical properties, native nesting (no BEM `&__` / `&--`). No SASS.

This is required project CSS policy—not optional guidance.
